		<p class="bodytext">Cultural events are at the centre of the Resurgence. Cultural events <br/> 
			comprises a whole world of various dance competitions like hip-hop,<br/> 
			regionals, street dance and many more. On the other hand in theatrical <br/> 
			events participants show their acting skills in competitions like skit, mime, street play to name a few. And don't forget the awesome world of music presented by the students which includes western, hindi as well as regional<br/>
			 music competitions.
