	<div class="textblock nocaption"><h2>SMVDU, an University gifted by nature</h2><p class="bodytext">Probably the best part of SMVDU is its natural surroundings and ecosystem. Being blessed in the foothills of Shri Mata Vaishno Devi Shrine and Trikuta hills, SMVDU provides the best possible environment for the students to nourish and hone their skills in a calm and serene surroundings. Every evening is a holiday in itself and students at SMVDU enjoy it at its best.</p></div></div>

<div class="box doubleBlock2 horizontal " style="display:none;"><div class="mainImage slideshow"><img class="main" src="library/YARUBAR_BLADE-W5HW.jpg"/><img class="loader" src="img/loader2.gif" width="14" height="14"/></div><div class="textblock nocaption"><a class="h2_a" href="/en/yarubar/kef-blade"><h2>KEF Blade</h2></a><p class="bodytext">The world&rsquo;s first &#39;single apparent source speaker&#39; by <a href="http://www.kef.com/html/us/index.html" target="_blank">KEF</a> delivers a sound so<br />
precise, it&rsquo;s virtually indistinguishable from a live performance. Unlike&nbsp;conventional speakers, Blade&rsquo;s revolutionary driver configuration speaks&nbsp;to you with a single voice. It radiates sound waves at all frequencies in&nbsp;perfect harmony. Its new patented technologies, are the result of KEF&rsquo;s&nbsp;three-year research and development programme. Priced around US$30,000 you may purchase yours&nbsp;<a href="http://www.kefdirect.com/kef-blade.html" target="_blank">directly</a> from KEF.<br />
</p></div><div class="clear"></div></div>

<div class="box doubleBlock2 vertical bottom" style="display:none;"><div class="mainImage slideshow"><img class="main" src="img/DSC05707.jpg"/><img class="main" src="img/IMG_0147.jpg"/><img class="main" src="img/DSC_2452.jpg"/><img class="main" src="library/PRINCIPLE04-1LAH.jpg"/><img class="loader" src="img/loader2.gif" width="14" height="14"/><div class="prev"><div class="arrow"><img src="library/slideshow_prev.png" width="19" height="18"/></div></div><div class="next"><div class="arrow"><img src="img/slideshow_next.png" width="19" height="18"/></div></div></div><div class="textblock nocaption"><a class="h2_a" href="/en/yarubar/the-principle-hong-kong"><h2>The Principal, Hong Kong</h2></a><p class="bodytext">Featuring the cuisine of head chef Jonay Armas, <a href="http://www.theprincipal.com.hk/" target="_blank">The Principal</a> is all about the exploration of seriously new tastes, textures and techniques using the finest ingredients and methods - both traditional and innovative. The Principal celebrates fine dining that is spontaneous and unchained by convention.&nbsp;Imagine bite-sized pieces of smoked eel garnished with herring roe then carefully arranged around blocks of aloe vera jelly and tomatoes cooked three ways. A quenelle of pineapple ice cream sits in the centre of the plate over a shallow pool of palate-cleansing fennel sauce. It&rsquo;s a colourful canvas of contrasting textures, temperatures and flavours.&nbsp;The carefully curated Wine Atlas is amazing too and contains over 750 labels from both old and new worlds, including some very unexpected countries, with the oldest vintage dating back to 1901.<br />
</p></div></div>

